{"id":146934,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/德国政府称开放就业市场无需担忧/","date":"2011-04-23T17:30:18Z","modified":"2011-04-23T17:30:18Z","title":"德国政府称开放就业市场无需担忧","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">今年</span>5<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span>1<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日起，德国将向东欧国家开发就业市场。德国劳工部长冯·德·莱恩</span>(Ursula von der Leyen)<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">认为，人们无需为此担心，就业市场不会受到太大冲击。但是冯·德·莱恩也指出，底层劳工市场依然会有一些风险，这也验证了行业最低工资标准的必要性。</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">联邦劳动总局估计，开放德国就业市场后，每年将相应增加约</span>14<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万移民。德国经济界对此持欢迎态度，表示自由开放的劳动力市场能够填补德国经济对专业人才的需求。而德国服务行业工会则警告称，在那些还没有引入最低工资制度的行业可能会面临工资倾销。</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">东欧地区</span><span>8</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">个国家的公民将在今年</span><span>5</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>1</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日获准在欧盟境内自由迁徙就业，但</span><span>2007</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年新加入欧盟的罗马尼亚与保加利亚暂不在此列。</span></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com\"><img src=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com/images/1x1.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"ftrf - full text rss\" /></a><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15026017%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E5%BE%B7%E5%9B%BD%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A7%B0%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E5%B0%B1%E4%B8%9A%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E6%97%A0%E9%9C%80%E6%8B%85%E5%BF%A7\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙